name: Android-styler
body:
## Android Styler

Convert android style in text-section in layout, to style description in styles.xml.

## Example

![Example](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/muzavan/android-styler/master/example.png)

## Usage

Clone this repo.

`git clone https://github.com/muzavan/android-styler`

Go to directory.

`cd android-styler`

Open index.html in your browser. Should be working.

## Future Works

Create as add-ons in your favorite editor.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
